summary:

Jonah arrives with...
body:
Jarty Prom Moodboard


Prom HeadCanons:

Jonah brought up the idea of prom with a frisbee promposal which made Marty laugh so hard

Jonah arrives with Marty fav flowers and Martys mum insist she gets a photo with her “baby looking so cute” hence Marty grumpy face, which leads to Jonah teasing him all the way to car

Marty puts a corsage on Jonahs suit and they drive off

They jam out to 90s tunes in the car and scream it at the top of their lungs and just talk a lot

When they get to the prom venue they immediately have a punch contest to see who can chug the most Hawaiin punch, Jonah loses and pretends to be upset about it

So Marty holds his hand, and gives him a kiss “happy now” and Jonah blushing so cute

After an hour of dancing wildly to upbeat songs, the dj puts on a slow song, and they slow dance really close together and happily, Jonah kisses Marty on the lips

After the prom over they drive around town and Jonah lets Marty use him camera to take pictures of them and their surroundings

They get so caught up in watching the stars and talking that when Jonah drops Marty off it almost 2 am

Marty Mom scolds Jonah but not really, and Marty laughs while Jonah looks traumatized

Marty texts and facetimes Jonah till 5 before he falls asleep, and Jonah just smiles softly and ends the face time but not before taking a screenshot and changing his wallpaper to a sleeping Marty

( @judgemental-llama hope you dont mind these in one big post was too lazy to make separate posts)
